        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "When you Activate a nap gas dispenser, you can either place it in an adjacent space or toss it up to 30 feet away. Once you\u2019ve done so, the metallic canister instantly disperses knockout gas in a 15-foot burst. Creatures in the area must attempt a DC 23 Fortitude save, with the following results. This is a poison and incapacitation effect.",
